data.title: 4DMT partners with Otsuka Pharma to develop 4D-150 for wet AMD & DME in Asia-Pacific region, incl. Japan.
data.description: Emeryville, California - On October 30, 2025, 4D Molecular Therapeutics (Nasdaq: FDMT, 4DMT) disclosed a significant strategic alliance with Otsuka Pharmaceutical Co., Ltd. (Otsuka). This partnership aims to collaborate on the development and distribution of 4D-150, a potential treatment for wet age-related macular degeneration (wet AMD) and diabetic macular edema (DME) in the larger Asia-Pacific (APAC) area, which includes Japan. 4D-150 holds promise to revolutionize treatment approaches and deliver substantial advantages to patients. This move signifies a notable milestone for both companies in the biotechnology sector.

data.title: Kelvin Peng discusses AI in e-commerce on Phoenix Weekly, Oct 30, 2025. Shoplazza's CPO highlights smarter experience.
data.description: On October 30, 2025, Kelvin Peng, the Chief Product Officer at Shoplazza, a prominent e-commerce platform, participated in a discussion on Three Talks by Phoenix Business Weekly. This episode featured Peng alongside Yao Xiang, the General Manager for Greater China at Checkout.com. The conversation delved into various aspects of the e-commerce industry and garnered attention from a significant audience.
